<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Opinion Matters! Help Shape Healthcare & Win!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #0056b3;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .hero img {
            max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .prize-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 2px dashed #28a745;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .prize-section img {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .prize-section h2 {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .prize-section p {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .survey-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.4em;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .survey-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .instructions {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
        }
        .testimonials {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .testimonial-card {
            background-color: #e0f7fa;
            border-left: 5px solid #007bff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        .testimonial-card p {
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .testimonial-card .author {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: right;
            color: #0056b3;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                width: 95%;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            .prize-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.7em;
            }
            .prize-section p {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }
            .survey-button {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                padding: 12px 25px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="hero">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150/007bff/ffffff?text=Health+Icon" alt="Healthcare Icon">
            <h1>Your Voice Shapes the Future of Healthcare!</h1>
            <p>Share your insights and help us improve healthcare services.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Why Participate?</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em;">We're conducting a vital survey to understand your experiences and perspectives on healthcare. Your honest feedback is invaluable in identifying areas for improvement and innovation. As a thank you for your time and valuable contribution, you'll be entered into a drawing for a fantastic healthcare-related prize!</p>

        <div class="prize-section">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100/28a745/ffffff?text=Prize+Icon" alt="Prize Icon">
            <h2>Win a [Specific Healthcare Prize, e.g., $200 Wellness Gift Card, Smart Health Tracker, or a Year's Subscription to a Health App]!</h2>
            <p>Complete our short survey, and you'll be automatically entered into a draw to win an exciting prize that promotes your well-being!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="instructions">
            <h3>It's quick and easy!</h3>
            <p>The survey should take approximately <strong>5-7 minutes</strong> to complete. Your responses are completely anonymous and will be aggregated with others to provide a comprehensive overview.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
            <a href="#survey-link" class="survey-button">Start the Survey Now!</a>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #6c757d;">Click the button above to begin. You will be redirected to our secure survey platform.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonials">
            <h2>What Our Participants Say:</h2>

            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"I was happy to share my thoughts. It's reassuring to know my feedback can make a difference in healthcare. Plus, the chance to win a great prize was a nice bonus!"</p>
                <div class="author">- Sarah K., New York</div>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"The survey was straightforward and covered important topics. I feel more connected to the healthcare community knowing my opinion is valued."</p>
                <div class="author">- Michael R., California</div>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"It only took a few minutes, and I learned a bit more about the healthcare landscape while contributing to something meaningful. I'm excited about the prize draw!"</p>
                <div class="author">- Emily L., Texas</div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023

