<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Important Notice Regarding Your Merchandise</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
  }
  .container {
    width: 80%;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }
  h1 {
    color: #d9534f; /* Reddish color for urgency */
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .highlight {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #f0ad4e; /* Amber color for attention */
  }
  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #5cb85c; /* Green button */
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 15px;
  }
  .button:hover {
    background-color: #4cae4c;
  }
  .footer {
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    color: #777;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Important Notice: Your Merchandise is Currently Held</h1>

    <p>Dear [Customer Name],</p>

    <p>This email is to inform you that your recent merchandise order, [Order Number], is currently being held due to outstanding fees. This may include, but is not limited to, unpaid shipping costs, taxes, or other applicable charges associated with your order.</p>

    <p>We understand this may be an inconvenience, and we apologize for any disruption this may cause. To ensure you receive your items as quickly as possible, please take the following steps to resolve this matter:</p>

    <p><strong>How to Resolve This Issue:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Review Your Outstanding Fees:</strong> You can view a detailed breakdown of the outstanding fees by logging into your account on our website and navigating to the "Order History" or "Invoices" section.</li>
      <li><strong>Make a Payment:</strong> To settle the outstanding balance, please click the secure payment link below:
        <br>
        <a href="[Payment Link]" class="button">Pay Outstanding Fees Now</a>
      </li>
      <li><strong>Confirmation:</strong> Once your payment has been successfully processed, your merchandise will be released and prepared for shipment. You will receive a separate confirmation email with tracking information once your order is on its way.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="highlight">Please note that failure to resolve these outstanding fees within [Number] days may result in the cancellation of your order and a full refund, minus any applicable restocking or administrative fees.</p>

    <p>If you believe this notice is in error, or if you have already made a payment, please contact our customer support team immediately at [Customer Support Email] or call us at [Customer Support Phone Number] with your payment details or any relevant information.</p>

    <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>

    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p>The [Your Company Name] Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; [Current Year] [Your Company Name]. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>[Your Company Address]</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
